tags.name: Motel Antika
tags.note: Motel Antika has a restaurant closed to the building where guests can eat with low prizes. Motel and restaurant Antika has a mini zoo in the backyard which can be visited anytime while restaurant is open. They serve traditional food, pan food.

tags.name: Restaurant Vala e Drinit
tags.note: Vala e Drinit is located near the source of White Drin, which provides fresh and delicious food and drink. You can enjoy there a friendly atmosphere and have in front an amazing view.

tags.description: Serves soft drinks, coffee. Decent toilet available. (July 2023)
tags.name: Simoni Kafe
Restaurant Ujëvara e Drinit
tags.note: Restaurant Ujvara e Drinit is located in a beautiful and enormous area. If you sit outside you can see the source of the White Drin, which is an amazing view of waterfall. There you can taste delicious trout fish and stay comfortable.

tags.name: Restaurant Koha e Re
tags.note: Koha e Re has a lovely environment which offers halls for wedding ceremony, conference rooms. They have a diverse cuisine, delicious dishes with very economic prices.

tags.name: Restaurant Iliria
tags.note: Restaurant Iliria is such a delectable place to spend some time. You can taste great food and enjoy your time near the city of Decan. There you can arrange a party or a ceremony, because it has a large space and lovely décor to make your day more special.

tags.name: Restaurant Moronica
tags.note: This restaurant is located 662 meters above sea level. Its open and spacious premises create a beautiful atmosphere. Surrounded by nature is set on top of a mountain from where you can see the city of Peja.

tags.name: Konaku
tags.note: Restaurant Konaku it is a place where visitors and locals go to get massive portions of good, home-cooked traditional food.

tags.description: Serves soft drinks, beer, food. Decent toilets. (survey July 2023)
